 the work of this intriguing artist and the intertwined histories of film and photography.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 7aART / General.2bisacsh1 aJenkins, Bruce, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMcelheny, Josiah, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSaunders, Matt, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Chicago Press eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2013z978311063538640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780226042916423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780226042916.jpg  a978-3-11-063538-6  University of Chicago Press eBook-Package Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aGBV-deGruyter-alles